{"tid":439262,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求巴打覆 呢份工有冇伏","createTime":"2017-10-17T15:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T16:22:32.000Z","uid":37035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37b93972b3cb1008b7b1fe4b3396c67dd7eeb857","tid":439262,"uid":37035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"第一次借人ac出post<br />\n有錯請輕力插<br />\n<br />\n由於小弟失業左一排<br />\n最近使哂積蓄淨返屋企三包出前一丁做最後食糧<br />\n老母做埋嫦娥日日問我幾時返工<br />\n咁啱我經過見到呢份工人工好似幾好<br />\n但又擔心唔知要做乜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/234635_aa4284b7f8c9f8b767abfaaf73174b2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F234635_aa4284b7f8c9f8b767abfaaf73174b2a.jpg&h=51c9a5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想黎問下有冇巴打做過或者做緊呢份工<br />\n工作內容係要做乜<br />\n會唔會要踢人入會/呃阿婆按左佢層樓咁架<br />\n如果唔係要做陰質野我會去試下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed00902d00902bc24ff6898e6b7cd67ae161a88a","tid":439262,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c10d6a0f338efcf32a56c3cd57ccd1d245fdc4","tid":439262,"uid":37035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n哂<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>晒</strong></span><br />\n淨返<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>剩返</strong></span><br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>噉</strong></span><br />\n黎<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n架<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>㗎</strong></span><br />\n陰質<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>陰騭</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住我係認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪個個連登巴打都對正字咁高要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為唔用吾系甘牙已經得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fc6ad688a28cbaed063905cc4b9031bdb5d411","tid":439262,"uid":128850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"幫推一下"},{"pid":"c40fd6fe553154c28d218e9bc7d24bc39e461dff","tid":439262,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:12:03.000Z","msg":"入去做 見有問題就即刻走人"},{"pid":"78eef584eb29176059f61b5881285cc0f48a5e84","tid":439262,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n哂<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>晒</strong></span><br />\n淨返<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>剩返</strong></span><br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>噉</strong></span><br />\n黎<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n架<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>㗎</strong></span><br />\n陰質<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>陰騭</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f6f51ac29169f2dde8c2d6e26e988958fd3bfa","tid":439262,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"100/小時<br />\n<br />\n我做it狗都係34.5/小時<br />\n<br />\n自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1cf09